---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import '../../styles/global.css';
---

<Layout title="커뮤니티 게시판">
  <div class="board-container">
    <div class="board-header">
      <h1>커뮤니티 게시판</h1>
      <p class="subtitle">Sudoremove 커뮤니티에서 자유롭게 소통하세요</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="board-actions">
      <a href="https://github.com/orgs/sudormrf-run/discussions" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="action-card main-link">
        <span class="icon">💬</span>
        <h2>GitHub Discussions 바로가기</h2>
        <p>커뮤니티의 모든 토론을 확인하고 참여하세요</p>
        <span class="arrow">→</span>
      </a>
      
      <div class="sub-actions">
        <a href="https://github.com/orgs/sudormrf-run/discussions/new/choose" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="action-card new-post">
          <span class="icon">✍️</span>
          <h3>새 글 작성</h3>
          <p>질문, 아이디어, 프로젝트 공유</p>
        </a>
        
        <a href="https://github.com/orgs/sudormrf-run/discussions/categories/announcements" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="action-card announcements">
          <span class="icon">📢</span>
          <h3>공지사항</h3>
          <p>중요한 소식과 업데이트</p>
        </a>
        
        <a href="https://github.com/orgs/sudormrf-run/discussions/categories/q-a" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="action-card qna">
          <span class="icon">🙏</span>
          <h3>Q&A</h3>
          <p>궁금한 점을 물어보세요</p>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="board-info">
      <h2>💡 커뮤니티 이용 안내</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>GitHub 계정으로 로그인하면 모든 기능을 사용할 수 있습니다</li>
        <li>마크다운 문법을 사용하여 코드, 이미지, 링크 등을 공유할 수 있습니다</li>
        <li>서로 존중하며 건설적인 피드백을 공유해주세요</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>

<style>
  body {
    background: #0d030f !important;
    color: #ffffff !important;
  }
  
  .board-container {
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 2rem;
  }

  .board-header {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  h1 {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    color: #fd7318;
  }

  .subtitle {
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    color: #b8b8b8;
  }

  .board-actions {
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  .action-card {
    display: block;
    background: #1a0f1f;
    border: 1px solid #333;
    border-radius: 0.75rem;
    padding: 2rem;
    text-decoration: none;
    color: #ffffff;
    position: relative;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .action-card:hover {
    border-color: #fd7318;
    transform: translateY(-4px);
    box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(253, 115, 24, 0.2);
  }

  .main-link {
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1a0f1f, #251730);
  }

  .main-link::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    right: 0;
    height: 3px;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, #fd7318, #43d6a8);
  }

  .sub-actions {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
    gap: 1rem;
  }

  .action-card .icon {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    display: block;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .action-card h2 {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    color: #fd7318;
  }

  .action-card h3 {
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    color: #43d6a8;
  }

  .action-card p {
    color: #b8b8b8;
    margin: 0;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
  }

  .arrow {
    position: absolute;
    bottom: 1.5rem;
    right: 1.5rem;
    font-size: 2rem;
    color: #fd7318;
    transition: transform 0.3s ease;
  }

  .action-card:hover .arrow {
    transform: translateX(5px);
  }

  .board-info {
    background: #1a0f1f;
    border: 1px solid #333;
    border-radius: 0.75rem;
    padding: 2rem;
  }

  .board-info h2 {
    color: #fd7318;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .board-info ul {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .board-info li {
    padding: 0.5rem 0;
    padding-left: 1.5rem;
    position: relative;
    color: #b8b8b8;
  }

  .board-info li:before {
    content: "✓";
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    color: #43d6a8;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .board-container {
      padding: 1rem;
    }

    .frame-header {
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 0.5rem;
    }

    iframe {
      min-height: 600px;
    }
  }
</style>